Package com.epoch.chem

Classes for manipulating chemical structures and calculating their properties.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChemUtils
    Holds utility chemistry functions involving manipulations of molecules (e.g., getting enantiomers, adding explicit H atoms), electron-counting methods.
    ElectronMatcher
    Alters normal JChem matching behavior so that corresponding atoms in the query and target must have the same number of unshared electrons.
    ExplicitHMatcher
    Alters normal JChem matching behavior so that corresponding atoms in the query and target must have the same number of explicit H atoms.
    FnalGroupDef
    Defines a functional group.
    Formula
    Holds a formula.
    FormulaFunctions
    Contains formula matching and calculation functions.
    MolCompare
    Contains molecule matching methods.
    MolString
    Holds molecule format interconversions and manipulations of graphical objects in MRV documents.
    Normalize
    Contains molecule normalization methods.
    pKaFunctions
    Contains methods for calculating pKas.
    StereoFunctions
    Contains stereoisomer generation and manipulation functions.
    VectorMath
    Methods for doing 3D geometry such as calculating dihedral angles or bond angles.
    WavyBondMatcher
    Alters normal JChem matching behavior so that a query wavy bond matches only to a target wavy bond, but a query single bond continues to match to any target bond.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    FormulaException
    Thrown when there is an error parsing the molecular formula.
    MolCompareException
    Thrown when a MolCompare method can't import a String representation of a molecule or when a MolSearch fails.
    WedgeException
    Thrown when there is an error involving wedge bonds.
